episodes.title: Queer Eye for the Lambda Chi
episodes.plot: A kindhearted crew of fraternity brothers go from boys to men as they spruce up their house and sharpen their hosting skills for an important event.

episodes.title: Superfan Steph
episodes.plot: A sports superfan who hides behind hates and logos sets a goal to become a better partner for the woman she loves before they move into their new home.

episodes.title: Speedy for Life
episodes.plot: After a traumatic accident, a young man wants to inspire others but hides his own sadness. Can the Fab Five - and a returning hero - help him open up?

episodes.title: Jenni Seckel's Diary
episodes.plot: The Fab Five help a selfless educator who goes all in for her students and co-workers show herself some love and see that she's more than her job.

episodes.title: Deli Dan is a Dream Man
episodes.plot: A gruff deli owner with a big personality pours all of his energy into his business, but his girlfriend is craving more of his time and attention.

episodes.title: Ms. Mary Quite Contrary
episodes.plot: A hardworking hero who spent years in prison and helps the formerly incarcerated rebuild their lives is ready to move forward and embrace her own future.

episodes.title: Sowing the Seeds
episodes.plot: A pioneering farmer who feeds his community with fresh, healthy food struggles to see his own self-worth. Enter the Fab Five to help grow his confidence.
